```

## ğŸ”§ Features

- ğŸš€ **Multiple Project Types** - 10+ extension templates for different use cases
- âš¡ **Modern Tooling** - Express.js with security middleware, Flask with best practices
- ï¿½ **Security First** - CORS, rate limiting, helmet security headers included
- ğŸ“¦ **Auto Dependencies** - Automatic NPM/pip package installation
- ğŸŒ **HTTPS Development** - Secure development server out of the box
